channel.title: My 508 HD Ip Changing Client [Open Source]
channel.description:
Okay, lulz. First of all, I made this whilst I was offline. I used Cellkyborgs HD loader, cuz I have no idea how to get one.
All of this info is in the info folder.
Credits&Shoutz to the following people:
GwasDdos/Jerry, he was the only person that would text with me whilst I was offline.
Cellkyborg, for the actual loader and the basic "loader.java" I started with, obviously couldn't have done it without you man thanks alot. :)
Dan(GhostSnyper), he prolly shouldn't be in here but SHOUTZ woot.
JaGeX - Love the cache&textures.. Much luv<3 ;)
My gf, for motivating me and telling me Pat was a better coder, really got me going. ;)
Jordan, for always being there insulting me, SHOUTZ woot.
Piff(Jeff), for also being there with jordan and teh insults. Shoutz.
My brother for getting a DUI. (Driving under the influence, LOL)
My mom for bailing him out. SHOUTZ.
My dealer, for supplying me with the best greenbud around whilst I was disconnected from the web. Ftw.
My dad for co-signing for this computer. (Lulz)
Notepad++(I hate this IDE, but I couldn't dev this in netbeans for some reason. (library issues))
Updates:
Added JFrame Added JMenuBar Added IP Changer & option selector. (Main.java & NewIP.java) Added Sites Added Music using JLayer, see JLayer info.txt. Added screenshots Added License Added the loader as a library, as apposed to all those gunked up class files Seperated .class & .java files to ..\.\com\ & ..\.\bin\ Added linux run methods Added JLayer as a library
Picz0rz:
[IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/15yt5km.png[/img]
A better picture:
[IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/ab7583.png[/img]
Downloadness: [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?xjmo2nqfz3y]Click here ;o[/url][/quote]
